  <entry>
    <title>解析Go Slice</title>
    <url>/2020/05/04/%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90Go-Slice/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>slice（切片）是Go中一种基本的数据结构，是对数组的一个连续片段的<strong>引用</strong>，这个片段可以是整个数组，也可以是数组的子集。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="数据结构"><a href="#数据结构" class="headerlink" title="数据结构"></a>数据结构</h2><p>切片本身并不是动态数组或者数组指针。它内部实现的数据结构<strong>通过指针引用底层数组</strong>，设定相关属性（长度和容量）将数据读写操作限定在指定区域内。</p>
<p>数组一经初始化，长度就固定了；切片的长度可以在运行时修改，可以看成是长度可变的数组，应该注意的是切片的底层其实就是数组。</p>
<p>slice的数据结构定义如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> slice <span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">	array unsafe.Pointer</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">len</span>   <span class="keyword">int</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">cap</span>   <span class="keyword">int</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>切片的结构体由3部分构成，array是指向一个数组的指针，len 代表当前切片的长度，cap 是当前切片的容量。cap 总是大于等于 len 的。</p>
<h2 id="创建与初始化"><a href="#创建与初始化" class="headerlink" title="创建与初始化"></a>创建与初始化</h2><h3 id="使用make"><a href="#使用make" class="headerlink" title="使用make"></a>使用make</h3><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 创建一个长度和容量都为3的切片</span></span><br><span class="line">slice := <span class="built_in">make</span>([]<span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 创建一个长度为3，容量为5的切片</span></span><br><span class="line">slice := <span class="built_in">make</span>([]<span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="number">3</span>， <span class="number">5</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="空切片"><a href="#空切片" class="headerlink" title="空切片"></a>空切片</h3><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> slice []<span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="comment">//如果指定了大小，则为创建数组</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="从数组或切片生成新的切片"><a href="#从数组或切片生成新的切片" class="headerlink" title="从数组或切片生成新的切片"></a>从数组或切片生成新的切片</h3><p>语法为：</p>
<figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">newSlice := oldSlice[开始位置：结束位置]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>示例：</p>
<figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a := [<span class="number">10</span>]<span class="keyword">int</span>&#123;<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">6</span>,<span class="number">7</span>,<span class="number">8</span>,<span class="number">9</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">slice := a[<span class="number">1</span>:<span class="number">8</span>] <span class="comment">//1,2,3,4,5,6,7</span></span><br><span class="line">newSlice := slice[<span class="number">0</span>:<span class="number">3</span>] <span class="comment">//1,2,3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="实际应用"><a href="#实际应用" class="headerlink" title="实际应用"></a>实际应用</h2><h3 id="copy"><a href="#copy" class="headerlink" title="copy()"></a>copy()</h3><p>可以将一个slice拷贝到另一个slice中。</p>
<figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">copy</span><span class="params">(dst, src []Type)</span> <span class="title">int</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这表示将src slice拷贝到dst slice，src比dst长，就截断，src比dst短，则只拷贝src那部分。copy的返回值是拷贝成功的元素数量，所以也就是src slice或dst slice中最小的那个长度。</p>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s1 := []<span class="keyword">int</span>&#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">s2 := <span class="built_in">make</span>([]<span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line">s3 := <span class="built_in">make</span>([]<span class="keyword">int</span>,<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">num := <span class="built_in">copy</span>(s2, s1)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">copy</span>(s3,s1)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(num)   <span class="comment">// 3</span></span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(s2)    <span class="comment">// [1,2,3,0,0]</span></span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(s3)    <span class="comment">// [1,2]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="append"><a href="#append" class="headerlink" title="append()"></a>append()</h3><p>可以使用append()函数对slice进行扩展，因为它追加元素到slice中，所以一定会增加slice的长度。如果增加后的长度超出的slice的容量，则要对slice进行扩容，也就是申请新的容量更大数组给切片。具体策略以后会专门讲一下。</p>
<figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> s []<span class="keyword">int</span></span><br><span class="line">newS := <span class="built_in">append</span>(s, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(s)</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(newS)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="栈与队列"><a href="#栈与队列" class="headerlink" title="栈与队列"></a>栈与队列</h3><p>Go中没有实现栈与队列的数据结构，通过操作slice可以实现它们的功能。</p>
<h4 id="栈"><a href="#栈" class="headerlink" title="栈"></a>栈</h4><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> stack []element</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// push</span></span><br><span class="line">stack = <span class="built_in">append</span>(stack, x)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// top</span></span><br><span class="line">top := stack[<span class="built_in">len</span>(stack)<span class="number">-1</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// pop</span></span><br><span class="line">stack = stack[:<span class="built_in">len</span>(s)<span class="number">-1</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="队列"><a href="#队列" class="headerlink" title="队列"></a>队列</h4><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> queue []element</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// push</span></span><br><span class="line">queue = <span class="built_in">append</span>(queue, x)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// top</span></span><br><span class="line">top := queue[<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// pop</span></span><br><span class="line">queue = queue[<span class="number">1</span>:]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Go</category>
      </categories>
